    MaterialTheme.getMotionScheme returns androidx.compose.material3.MotionScheme,
    a Kotlin-internal interface (visibility="" in api.xml). The binding generator
    skips emitting the interface but still emits this getter referencing it,
    producing CS0234. The method was never emitted on main either (the parameter
    type androidx.compose.runtime.Composer was unresolvable when Compose.Runtime
    shipped as an empty managed facade), so removing it keeps API surface unchanged.
  -->
  <remove-node path="/api/package[@name='androidx.compose.material3']/class[@name='MaterialTheme']/method[@name='getMotionScheme']" />
</metadata>
